layers.nm: STATISTICS OF MURDERS IN OMSK FROM 2015-2022 • The most crime-ridden district is Oktyabrsky (10.2 crimes per 100,000 people) • The most dangerous district is also Oktyabrsky (5.1 murders per 100,000 people) • The most rapes occur in Leninsky district (2.9 per 100,000 people) • The least amount of thefts occur in Leninsky district (422.6 per 100,000 people) • The most drugs are found in Central district (209.6 cases per 100,000 people) • In 2021, there were no reported rapes in Oktyabrsky district • In 2016, there were a record 22 murders in Central district • The most crime-ridden year in Omsk was 2017 (93 crimes) • The least amount of rapes in Omsk occurred in 2022 (10 crimes) • 386 people have been killed in Omsk in the last 8 years.
